    "question": "How do you say 'hello' in Ukrainian?",
    "correctAnswer": "{{uk-UA|Привіт|Pryvit|pry-VIT}}",
    "incorrectAnswers": [
      "{{uk-UA|До побачення|Do pobachennya|DO po-ba-CHEN-nya}}",
      "{{uk-UA|Дякую|Dyakuyu|DYA-kuyu}}",
      "{{uk-UA|Будь ласка|Bud laska|BUD LAS-ka}}"
    ],
    "explanation": "'Pryvit' is the casual hello. Formal: 'Dobroho dnya' (good day).",
